他们在跑！

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:10.400
Stay down and don't move.
趴下，不要动。

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:12.400
Tripple, what are we doing?
特里普，我们在做什么？

00:19:12.400 --> 00:19:15.400
Is that an intermission to the world?
这是世界的插曲吗？

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:20.400
Freeze right there!
别动！

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:22.400
