[枪声]

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:24.400
[screams]
[尖叫声]

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:26.400
[screams]
[尖叫声]

00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:30.400
- Take your mask off! - What happened to Tori?
