6,000 gallons of compressed carbon dioxide.
是6000加仑的压缩二氧化碳。

00:20:03.400 --> 00:20:07.400
[radio chatter]
[无线电通话声]

00:20:07.400 --> 00:20:09.400
Where's this apple seat corner?
苹果座位角落在哪里？

00:20:09.400 --> 00:20:11.400
Right over there.
就在那边。

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:12.400
What's that?
那是什么？

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:14.400
Wild gas. That's for carbon dioxide.
那是二氧化碳的排气口。

00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:16.400
[radio chatter]
[无线电通话声]

00:20:16.400 --> 00:20:18.400
[tires squealing]
[轮胎摩擦声]

00:20:18.400 --> 00:20:36.400
What the hell?
怎么回事？

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:38.400
- What's going on? - I don't know.
- 发生什么事了？ - 我不知道。

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:41.400
