Cover your mouth.
捂住你的嘴。

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:30.400
One second, one second.
等一下，等一下。

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:32.400
Come, come this way.
过来，往这边走。

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:34.400
[shouting]
[喊叫]

