Let's go, let's run!
走吧，快跑！

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:42.400
[coughing]
[咳嗽]

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:44.400
Come, come, come, let's go.
来，来，来，我们走吧。

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:46.400
Help! Please help us!
救命！请救救我们！

00:21:46.400 --> 00:21:48.400
Please help us, please!
请救救我们，求求你们！

00:21:48.400 --> 00:21:52.400
Hurry, please!
快点，求求你们！

00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:54.400
[coughing]
[咳嗽]

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:58.400
[shouting]
[喊叫]

00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:00.400
[shouting]
[喊叫]

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:02.400
There's a guy over there, throw him in!
那边有个人，把他扔进去！

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:04.400
[shouting]
[喊叫]

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:10.400
I need help!
我需要帮助！

00:22:10.400 --> 00:22:12.400
Please help!
请帮帮我！

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:14.400
I can't get her to wake up!
我无法让她醒来！

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:16.400
Please hurry, hurry her!
请快点，快点救她！

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:18.400
She's not moving!
她不动了！

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:20.400
[crying]
[哭泣]

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:22.400
Please!
拜托！

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:24.400
[coughing]
[咳嗽]

00:22:24.400 --> 00:22:30.400
[coughing]
[咳嗽]

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:40.400
Clouds dissipated.
云层散去了。

00:22:40.400 --> 00:22:42.400
We got no fatalities, which is a minor miracle.
我们没有人员死亡，这算是个小小的奇迹。

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:44.400
What about the trooper that was shot?
那个被击中的士兵怎么样了？

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:46.400
He's gonna make it too. You good?
他也会没事的。你还好吗？

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:48.400
Yeah.
是啊。

00:22:48.400 --> 00:22:50.400
Look who we found hiding in the parking lot.
看看我們在停車場發現誰躲在那裡。

00:22:50.400 --> 00:22:52.400
Toy? It was so scary.
托伊？真是太可怕了。

00:22:52.400 --> 00:22:54.400
Where are they going? I don't know.
他們要去哪裡？我不知道。

00:22:54.400 --> 00:22:56.400
Cover. Oh my god, you're arresting me?
完了。天啊，你們要逮捕我？

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:58.400
Yeah, you helped out two fugitives.
沒錯，你幫助了兩個逃犯。

00:22:58.400 --> 00:23:00.400
You'll be helping yourself stay out of prison if you tell us where they're going.
如果你告訴我們他們要去哪，你就能幫自己避免坐牢。

00:23:00.400 --> 00:23:02.400
Okay, it's just Trevor, it's not Emma, they're looking for the pipeline.
好吧，只有崔佛，沒有艾瑪，他們在找輸油管。

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:04.400
What pipeline?
什麼輸油管？

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:06.400
And Steph has a CO2 pipeline around here.
史蒂夫在這附近有一條二氧化碳輸油管。

00:23:06.400 --> 00:23:08.400
I don't know, I don't know.
我不知道，我真的不知道。

00:23:08.400 --> 00:23:10.400
That's why Trevor wanted to kidnap the truck driver so that we could find out where he was going.
這就是為什麼崔佛想綁架卡車司機，這樣我們就能知道他要去哪。

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:16.400
Two people matching Trevor and Emma's description just hijacked a raft for it from a white female.
有兩個人符合崔佛和艾瑪的特徵，剛剛從一位白人女性那裡搶了一艘橡皮艇。

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:18.400
Yeah, Walmart parking lot 12 miles away.
對，在12英里外的沃爾瑪停車場。

00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:20.400
Check it out.
去查查看。

00:23:20.400 --> 00:23:22.400
Sit on that curb and don't say a word, I'm not done with you.
坐在那个路边，别说话，我还没跟你完事。

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:24.400
Okay, she's not wrong.
好吧，她没说错。

00:23:24.400 --> 00:23:26.400
Hen's step have just opened a CO2 pipeline that went online a week ago.
亨的步骤公司刚刚开通了一条一周前上线的二氧化碳管道。

00:23:26.400 --> 00:23:28.400
Then we need to get them to shut it down.
那我们需要让他们把它关掉。

00:23:28.400 --> 00:23:30.400
It could be Trevor and Emma's next target.
这可能是特雷弗和艾玛的下一个目标。

00:23:30.400 --> 00:23:32.400
Where's their HQ?
他们的总部在哪里？

00:23:32.400 --> 00:23:34.400
It's north in El Tuna on Highway 220.
在北部埃尔图纳的220号公路上。

00:23:34.400 --> 00:23:36.400
Text me the address and grill the hell out of her.
把地址发给我，然后好好拷问她。

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:38.400
I don't know anything else, I swear.
我发誓，我真的不知道别的了。

00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:40.400
Guess what, I don't believe a word that comes out of your mouth.
你知道吗，你说的每一句话我都不信。

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:42.400
Call me if you hear anything from Ray or Nina.
如果你从雷或妮娜那里听到什么，打电话给我。

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:44.400
Do you know how long it took us to get that thing up and running?
你知道我们花了多久才把那东西建好并运行起来吗？

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:46.400
Seven years.
七年。

00:23:46.400 --> 00:23:48.400
I'm not shutting it down now based on a hunch.
我现在不会因为一个猜测就把它关掉。

00:23:48.400 --> 00:23:50.400
It's more than a hunch, we know our two fugitives are targeting your pipeline.
这不仅仅是个猜测，我们知道那两个逃犯正瞄准你的管道。

00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:52.400
Where?
在哪裡？

00:23:52.400 --> 00:23:54.400
Don't know yet.
還不知道。

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:56.400
It's over 70 miles long, Agent Scott.
這條管道超過70英里長，史考特探員。

00:23:56.400 --> 00:23:58.400
Except for the part over near Everett that's still under construction.
除了靠近埃弗里特的那段還在建設中。

00:23:58.400 --> 00:24:00.400
Is that what you're talking about?
你說的是這個嗎？

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:04.400
It's just temporary until we finish.
這只是暫時的，等我們完工就好了。

00:24:04.400 --> 00:24:06.400
We're really doing the residents here a favor with our carbon capture.
我們的碳捕捉技術真的對這裡的居民有好處。

00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:08.400
What are you getting some kind of tax break for all this?
你做這些是不是為了某種稅收減免？

00:24:08.400 --> 00:24:10.400
Damn right.
當然是。

00:24:10.400 --> 00:24:12.400
It's called a 45Q, and after all the money we've invested,
這叫45Q稅收抵免，畢竟我們已經投入了大量資金，

00:24:12.400 --> 00:24:14.400
I need this pipeline to be operational before the whole company goes under.
我需要這條管道在整個公司倒閉之前投入運營。

00:24:14.400 --> 00:24:16.400
You know what happens if they blow that pipeline, right?
你知道如果他們炸掉那條管道會發生什麼嗎？

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.400
Lots of people will die.
很多人會死。

00:24:18.400 --> 00:24:20.400
My hands are really tied here.
我真的束手無策。

00:24:20.400 --> 00:24:22.400
Where are your priorities, man?
你的優先事項到底是什麼，老兄？

00:24:22.400 --> 00:24:24.400
If you don't shut down the pipeline,
如果你不关闭输油管道，

00:24:24.400 --> 00:24:26.400
